OL,6,FA robber who kept watch as her
OL,7,Faccomplice punched an elderly man 30
OL,8,Ftimes in a "shameful" attack in his
OL,9,Fown home has been jailed.
OL,11,FLauren Johnson, 29, and Andrew
OL,12,FRatcliffe knocked on the window of the
OL,13,F72-year-old's home in Scarborough to
OL,14,Fask for a glass of water.
OL,16,FRatcliffe then climbed in through the
OL,17,Fwindow and carried out what police
OL,18,Fcalled a "prolonged attack" and
OL,19,Fthreatened to kill him with a knife.
