OL,3,CRobber who kept watch during
OL,4,C'shameful' attack on elderly man jailed
OL,6,FJohnson closed the window to conceal
OL,7,Fthe victim's cries for help.
OL,9,FThe pair fled with just #13.
OL,11,FRatcliffe, 33, was later jailed for
OL,12,Feight-and-a-half years following the
OL,13,Fincident and two other burglaries.
OL,15,FJohnson has now been sentenced to two
OL,16,Fyears in prison after admitting
OL,17,Frobbery at York Crown Court.
