OL,3,CRobber who kept watch during
OL,4,C'shameful' attack on elderly man jailed
OL,6,FDet Con Sam Rivers, of Scarborough
OL,7,FCID, said: "This was clearly a planned
OL,8,Fand orchestrated robbery of a 72-year-
OL,9,Fold victim in his own home.
OL,11,F"It was a very frightening experience
OL,12,Ffor the poor man who has received
OL,13,Finjuries as a result of the attack."
OL,15,FHe added: "Offenders who commit this
OL,16,Fsort of crime are a scourge on
OL,17,Fsociety. It was a shameful and vicious
OL,18,Fattack and I'm glad our investigation
OL,19,Fbrought the perpetrators to justice."
